SUMMARY:Deadline to Register for the IU Global Career Accelerator Course
DESCRIPTION:The IU Global Career Accelerator course is a virtual\, 6-cred
 it tech course\, offering tracks in five different areas: Digital Marketi
 ng\, Data Analytics\, Web Development for Everyone\, Coding for Data\, an
 d Career Rotation. Registration is open for both the Summer 2026 and Fall
  2026 semesters. The deadline to apply for the Summer 2026 semester is Mo
 nday\, May 18\, which is also the first day of classes. Apply for the Fal
 l 2026 semester by August 24\, 2026.
